# Keep private financial data and secrets out of the knowledge graph.
#
# fixtures/ holds real SBI/Federal/IDFC/Suryoday/Zerodha/BHIM statements.
# Money data must never enter a graph that could later be fed to an LLM
# (CLAUDE.md hard invariant). Exclude the whole directory.
fixtures/

# Local secrets — never index env files or keys.
.env
.env*.local
*.pem

# Doc/markdown/yaml files need an LLM for *semantic* extraction; we run fully
# offline (no API key), so the corpus is code-only. To include docs later,
# remove the lines below and supply a backend key — but note CLAUDE.md and
# README.md describe this financial system, so weigh that before any LLM sees
# them. (90 code files are unaffected; none use these extensions.)
*.md
*.mdx
*.qmd
*.txt
*.rst
*.html
*.yaml
*.yml
*.pdf
